      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and mechanical integrity. This automobile offers a refined driving experience, balancing performance with proven reliability. Meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards, it stands as a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated balance of quality and value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
